*OOC Version of Fizzle's Rant*


I know I'm not supposed to respond to this shit, but if ya gotta problem with it fuck you and die. Besides, Laposn obviously doesn't know that this is an RP forum or he wouldn't post that shit up here. There's a difference between someone with bad RP writing skills and this bullshit. You (hopefully) didn't even make any fucking effort. 

Of course RP stories aren't what make or break a KAAOS wannabe, but Jesus fucking Christ! What the fuck is this? Do you think by being such a fucking dumbass that KAAOS will either feel sorry for you or keep you around longer? It was kinda funny to see someone as lame as you trying to get into KAAOS for a few days, but now your act is just getting fucking old.

-Fizzle
Your God
